Louise Redknapp was all smiles as she performed at Flackstock at Englefield House.The Eternal singer, 47, flashed her toned stomach in an oversized black suit.Louise cut a chic figure in a pair of high-waisted trousers which she paired with a cropped jacket of the same colour, flashing her washboard abs.The ex-wife of Jamie Redknapp wore her long blonde tresses in a slicked-back plait and donned a full-face of glamorous make-up. The festival was created by Caroline Flack's loved ones after the star took her own life in February 2020, aged 40.